            <h2 class="section-title">Built for Every South African Sector</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">Register your company and select your sector. UbuntuCRM automatically configures workflows, fields and reports specific to your industry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2">
                <div class="sector-card">
                    <div class="sector-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-car-side"></i></div>
